<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>LDAP on 元视角</title><link>https://blog.yuanpei.me/tags/ldap/</link><description>Recent content in LDAP on 元视角</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:42:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.yuanpei.me/tags/ldap/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>为你的服务器集成 LDAP 认证</title><link>https://blog.yuanpei.me/posts/integrate-ldap-authentication-for-your-server/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Nov 2022 12:49:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yuanpei.me/posts/integrate-ldap-authentication-for-your-server/</guid><description>回顾我这些年的工作经历，面向企业(2B)和面向用户(2C)的项目都曾接触过。我个人觉得，面向企业的项目更注重业务，参与决策的人数多、周期长，目的是为企业提供生产经营价值，如缩减成本、提升效率等等，而面向用户的项目更注重体验，参与决策的人数少</description></item></channel></rss>